ral radius of generalized distance matrix. Further, we\nobtain the generalized distance energy for bipartite graphs and trees. We prove\nthat the complete bipartite graph has minimum generalized distance energy among\nall connected bipartite graphs. Besides, for $ \\alpha\\in \\big(0,\n\\frac{2n}{3n-2}\\big) $, we show that the star graph has minimum generalized\ndistance energy among all trees.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 19 Jul 2021 21:20:51 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-07-21"}
