matic suppression of the noise\nphoton flux due to the filter proves its usefulness for experiments with\nsuperconducting quantum systems.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 20 Jul 2021 08:43:20 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 26 Jul 2021 22:11:05 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 28 Jul 2021 16:58:33 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Wed, 19 Jan 2022 14:23:36 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-01-20"}
