ight and round dwarfs and observe fewer\nnuclei in dwarfs with a faint centre and a small size. The colour of the galaxy\nnucleus shows no clear relation to the colour of the dwarf, in agreement with\nthe migration and wet migration nucleus formation scenarios. The catalogues of\nthe MATLAS dwarfs photometric and structural properties are provided.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 20 Jul 2021 09:52:47 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 16 Aug 2021 13:07:53 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-08-17"}
