sis will enable the design of complex MEMS devices by allowing to\nmodel the evolution of the etching process required for the release of\narbitrary structures made of oxide thin films deposited on top of STO.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 20 Jul 2021 12:21:38 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-07-21"}
