lems of mathematical physics\ndescribing, for instance, such phenomena as physical and chemical absorption\nwith diffusion, plasma states, stationary burning etc.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 20 Jul 2021 13:40:29 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 13 Jan 2022 15:58:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-01-14"}
